{{% examples %}}
## Example Usage
{{% example %}}

Get the reserved IP:

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as digitalocean from "@pulumi/digitalocean";

const config = new pulumi.Config();
const publicIp = config.requireObject("publicIp");
